</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 5:35
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='324960' id='t-324960'>(Applause)</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 5:39
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='328920' id='t-328920'>So in 2012, I started a company
to teach girls to code,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='333280' id='t-333280'>and what I found
