<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='352840' id='t-352840'>Code breaks and then it falls apart,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='355360' id='t-355360'>and it often takes many, many tries</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='357800' id='t-357800'>until that magical moment</span>
