<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='418160' id='t-418160'>Perfection or bust.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 7:13
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='422440' id='t-422440'>It turns out that our girls
